				"string" : "Oscar Nierstrasz — 10:30 via discord DM\nI read your additions to A Moldable Development Curriculum — that's really great! I have some questions about where material belongs best, but as we elaborate the teaching/learning units, I think that issue will solve itself. I pushed a few minor comments.\nDo you know what is meant by the “accordion” metaphor? Is it just widgets that can collapse, or is something else intended. There is a page in the GT Book called Accordion. Not sure if it's the same thing."
