				"string" : "### 4. In the Curriculum Context\n\nFor *A Moldable Development Curriculum*, this pairing becomes pedagogical:\n\n* Each learning unit is an *accordion topic* — depth unfolds through examples, exercises, and sideroads.\n* The overall curriculum can be browsed as *Miller Columns* — letting the learner trace conceptual dependencies and return to their personal starting point (“What does this mean for my project?”).\n\nThe “shortest path to self” then is:\n\n> The minimal sequence of conceptual expansions and navigations that connects new knowledge to one’s own practice.\n"
